{"text_id":101859,"tokens":["X","-","ray"," flares"," in"," Orion"," low"," mass"," stars"," have"," long"," been"," a"," topic"," of"," interest"," in"," the"," study"," of"," stellar"," astro","physics","."," These"," flares"," provide"," crucial"," insights"," into"," the"," magnetic"," activity"," and"," energy"," release"," mechanisms"," of"," low"," mass"," stars",","," and"," are"," particularly"," prevalent"," in"," young"," stellar"," populations"," such"," as"," those"," found"," in"," the"," Orion"," star","-","forming"," region","."," In"," this"," study",","," we"," aim"," to"," investigate"," the"," properties"," and"," frequency"," of"," X","-","ray"," flares"," in"," a"," sample"," of"," low"," mass"," stars"," in"," the"," Orion"," Nebula"," Cluster",".","\n\n","We"," utilized"," archival"," X","-","ray"," observations"," from"," the"," Chandra"," X","-","ray"," Observatory"," to"," identify"," and"," analyze"," X","-","ray"," flares"," from"," a"," sample"," of"," ","2","5","4"," low"," mass"," stars"," in"," the"," Orion"," Nebula"," Cluster","."," Our"," analysis"," included"," the"," measurement"," of"," flare"," properties"," such"," as"," peak"," flux",","," duration",","," and"," total"," energy",","," as"," well"," as"," the"," determination"," of"," flare"," frequency"," as"," a"," function"," of"," stellar"," parameters",".","\n\n","Our"," results"," reveal"," that"," X","-","ray"," flares"," in"," Orion"," low"," mass"," stars"," exhibit"," a"," wide"," range"," of"," properties",","," with"," peak"," fluxes"," ranging"," from"," $","1","0","^{","2","9","}$"," to"," $","1","0","^{","3","2","}$"," erg"," s","$^{-","1","}$,"," durations"," from"," a"," few"," hours"," to"," several"," days",","," and"," total"," energies"," from"," $","1","0","^{","3","0","}$"," to"," $","1","0","^{","3","5","}$"," erg","."," We"," also"," find"," that"," flare"," frequency"," is"," positively"," correlated"," with"," stellar"," rotation"," period",","," consistent"," with"," previous"," studies"," of"," solar"," and"," stellar"," flare"," activity","."," Furthermore",","," we"," observe"," a"," trend"," of"," increasing"," flare"," frequency"," with"," decreasing"," stellar"," mass",","," suggesting"," that"," lower"," mass"," stars"," may"," have"," stronger"," magnetic"," fields"," and"," more"," efficient"," energy"," release"," mechanisms",".","\n\n","These"," results"," contribute"," to"," our"," understanding"," of"," the"," magnetic"," activity"," and"," energy"," release"," processes"," in"," low"," mass"," stars",","," and"," highlight"," the"," importance"," of"," X","-","ray"," flares"," as"," a"," tool"," for"," studying"," stellar"," astro","physics","."," Future"," studies"," will"," aim"," to"," further"," investigate"," the"," physical"," mechanisms"," responsible"," for"," X","-","ray"," flares"," in"," low"," mass"," stars",","," and"," to"," explore"," the"," potential"," impacts"," of"," these"," flares"," on"," ex","oplan","etary"," atmospheres","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"mixtral-8x7b","label":1}